messages.content: The next election is a straight choice between a Labour government fighting for hardworking families and the NHS, or five more years of the Conservatives putting the most privileged first. Make your vote count.

messages.title: Personal Promise
messages.content: "I promise to fight every day for Dulwich and West Norwood, putting local residents and businesses first."
